articles.title: Texas floods leave at least 51 dead, 27 girls missing as rescuers search devastated landscape
articles.description: Catastrophic flash floods in central Texas have resulted in at least 51 fatalities, with 27 girls still missing as rescue teams continue their search efforts in the devastated area [2].

articles.title: Israel attacks more aid seekers in Gaza; 24 Palestinians killed today
articles.description: Israeli forces have attacked aid seekers in Gaza, resulting in the deaths of 24 Palestinians [1].

articles.title: Australian mushroom cook is convicted of triple murder after a fatal beef Wellington lunch
articles.description: An Australian woman has been convicted of triple murder following a fatal beef Wellington lunch [2, 3].
